extends layout.pug

block content
  include partials/icons.pug
  include partials/header.pug

  main#main
    section#top.relative.overflow-hidden(class='px-6 pt-32 pb-20 md:px-12 md:pt-44 md:pb-28 lg:px-20')
      .pointer-events-none.absolute.inset-0(aria-hidden='true')
        .hero-wash.absolute.rounded-full(class='left-1/2 top-0 -translate-x-1/2 h-160 w-275 opacity-60')
        .hero-grid-bg.absolute.inset-0(class='opacity-[0.06]')

      .relative.mx-auto(class='max-w-6xl')
        .grid.grid-cols-1(class='gap-12 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-16')
          .flex.flex-col(class='lg:col-span-8')
            span.eyebrow Services
            h1.font-serif.text-foreground.animate-fade-up(class='mt-8 text-[clamp(2.75rem,7.6vw,6rem)] leading-[0.94] tracking-tight')
              | SEO services for teams
              br
              span.serif-italic.text-spotlight that need the work done properly.
            p.text-muted-foreground.animate-fade-up.stagger-1(class='mt-8 max-w-2xl text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed')
              | I work across technical SEO, content systems, authority building, migrations,
              | programmatic pages, and reporting. Each service is built to turn search into
              | an operating channel, not another folder of recommendations.
            .flex.flex-wrap.items-center.animate-fade-up.stagger-2(class='mt-10 gap-4')
              a.hover-glow.group.inline-flex.items-center.rounded-full.bg-foreground.font-medium.text-background.transition-all.duration-300(
                href='#services-list'
                class='gap-2 h-12 pl-6 pr-5 text-sm hover:bg-foreground/90 active:scale-[0.98]'
              )
                | View services
                span.inline-flex.transition-transform.duration-300(class='group-hover:translate-x-0.5 group-hover:-translate-y-0.5')
                  +icon('arrow-down', 'h-4 w-4')
              a.group.inline-flex.items-center.rounded-full.border.border-border.font-medium.text-foreground.transition-colors.duration-300(
                href='#contact'
                class='gap-2 h-12 px-6 text-sm hover:border-foreground/40 hover:bg-foreground/3'
              )
                | Start a project
                span.inline-flex.transition-transform.duration-300(class='group-hover:translate-x-0.5 group-hover:-translate-y-0.5')
                  +icon('arrow-up-right', 'h-4 w-4')

          aside.flex.flex-col.justify-end(class='lg:col-span-4')
            .rounded-lg.border.border-border(class='bg-card/50 p-6 md:p-8')
              span.font-mono.uppercase.text-muted-foreground(class='text-[0.65rem] tracking-[0.22em]') Engagement style
              p.font-serif.text-foreground(class='mt-5 text-2xl tracking-[-0.015em] leading-tight')
                | Clear diagnosis, focused execution, and calm reporting while the work moves.
              dl.grid.grid-cols-1.border-t.border-border(class='mt-8 gap-5 pt-6')
                div
                  dt.font-mono.uppercase.text-muted-foreground(class='text-[0.65rem] tracking-[0.2em]') Best fit
                  dd.text-foreground(class='mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed') Growth teams, founders, and in house marketers who need SEO handled with care.
                div
                  dt.font-mono.uppercase.text-muted-foreground(class='text-[0.65rem] tracking-[0.2em]') Availability
                  dd.text-foreground(class='mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed') One or two projects at a time, so the work gets direct attention.

    section#services-list.relative(class='px-6 py-24 md:px-12 md:py-32 lg:px-20')
      .mx-auto(class='max-w-6xl')
        .flex.flex-col.border-b.border-border(class='gap-6 pb-12 md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between')
          div
            span.eyebrow The work
            h2.font-serif.text-foreground(class='mt-6 text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight leading-[1.05]')
              | Six ways to
              br
              span.serif-italic.text-muted-foreground improve organic growth.
          p.text-muted-foreground(class='max-w-md text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed')
            | Most projects start with one service and expand once the highest impact work is clear.
            | If the right answer is smaller than a retainer, I will say that too.

        ul.grid.grid-cols-1.bg-border(class='gap-px mt-px md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3')
          each service in services
            li.bg-background
              a.group.flex.h-full.flex-col.transition-colors.duration-300(
                href='/services/' + service.slug
                class='gap-6 p-8 lg:p-10 hover:bg-card'
              )
                .flex.items-start.justify-between
                  span.font-mono.text-muted-foreground(class='text-xs tracking-[0.18em]')= service.number
                  span.inline-flex.h-8.w-8.items-center.justify-center.rounded-full.text-muted-foreground.transition-all.duration-300(class='border border-transparent group-hover:border-border group-hover:text-foreground group-hover:-rotate-12')
                    +icon('arrow-up-right', 'h-3.5 w-3.5')
                h3.font-serif.text-foreground(class='text-2xl tracking-[-0.02em] leading-tight')= service.title
                p.text-muted-foreground.leading-relaxed(class='text-sm')= service.summary
                ul.flex.flex-col.border-t.border-border(class='mt-auto gap-2 pt-4')
                  each item in service.deliverables
                    li.flex.items-center.text-muted-foreground(class='gap-2 text-xs')
                      span.bg-primary(class='h-px w-3 opacity-70')
                      span= item

    section.relative.border-y.border-border(class='px-6 py-20 md:px-12 md:py-24 lg:px-20 bg-card/20')
      .mx-auto.grid.grid-cols-1(class='max-w-6xl gap-10 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-16')
        .flex.flex-col(class='lg:col-span-4')
          span.eyebrow How it usually starts
          h2.font-serif.text-foreground(class='mt-6 text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight leading-[1.05]')
            | First, we find
            br
            span.serif-italic.text-muted-foreground the real constraint.
        ol.grid.grid-cols-1(class='gap-px bg-border lg:col-span-8 md:grid-cols-3')
          li.bg-background(class='p-7')
            span.font-mono.text-primary(class='text-xs tracking-[0.18em]') 01
            h3.font-serif.text-foreground(class='mt-6 text-2xl tracking-[-0.015em]') Diagnose
            p.text-muted-foreground(class='mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed') We look at the site, the market, and the history before deciding what deserves effort.
          li.bg-background(class='p-7')
            span.font-mono.text-primary(class='text-xs tracking-[0.18em]') 02
            h3.font-serif.text-foreground(class='mt-6 text-2xl tracking-[-0.015em]') Prioritize
            p.text-muted-foreground(class='mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed') The plan is ordered by impact, effort, risk, and the team that has to ship it.
          li.bg-background(class='p-7')
            span.font-mono.text-primary(class='text-xs tracking-[0.18em]') 03
            h3.font-serif.text-foreground(class='mt-6 text-2xl tracking-[-0.015em]') Execute
            p.text-muted-foreground(class='mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed') We turn the strategy into shipped fixes, useful pages, clean reporting, and measured follow-through.

    include partials/contact.pug

  include partials/footer.pug
  include partials/scroll-to-top.pug
